Package: Max.WCST.R
Title: Tools for Simulating the Wisconsin Card Sorting Task
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: CodebyKazy
    person(given = "Max", 
           family = "Smecz", 
           email = "max.smecz@student.uva.nl", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simplified tools to simulate, score, and analyze the 
    Wisconsin Card Sorting Task (WCST), a classic cognitive assessment used to 
    evaluate executive functioning such as cognitive flexibility and rule-switching. 
    The package includes functions for generating decks, simulating user sessions, 
    scoring trials, and analyzing results.
